title: Hyper-V VM Running On Information
agents: windows
catalog: os/storage
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk

description:
 This check monitors which Hyper-V cluster node a virtual machine is currently running on.

 The check queries a Microsoft Hyper-V cluster via an agent plug-in and reports
 the current host node for each virtual machine and its state.

item:
 The name of the virtual machine

inventory:
 One service per virtual machine is created.
